erall efficiency, extend the learning curve, and affect the implementation project timeline.</p><p>In turn, if the vendor provides all the needed document forms for different scenarios from the service company lifecycle, it will make the adoption of the solution a lot easier. There are multiple features and business processes to automate, and it is great to get an opportunity to ask questions on how to do it faster and in a more efficient way.</p><B><U>Localization</U></B><br /><p>International software vendors often lack the proper support of local regulations. For example, in some Latin American countries, businesses are required to store all operations history. To send this data to regulators, the ERP should be integrated with the State Tax Service (facturacion electronica). Lots of well-known ERP solutions do not have this integration, while 1Ci:Drive does.</p>";s:21:"DATE_PUBLISH_FORMATED";s:10:"05.02.2021";s:17:"DATE_PUBLISH_DATE";s:10:"05.02.2021";s:17:"DATE_PUBLISH_TIME";s:5:"15:51";s:14:"DATE_PUBLISH_D";s:2:"05";s:14:"DATE_PUBLISH_M";s:2:"02";s:14:"DATE_PUBLISH_Y";s:4:"2021";}s:8:"PostPerm";s:1:"I";s:9:"urlToBlog";s:22:"/digital-intelligence/";s:9:"urlToPost";s:90:"/digital-intelligence/how-to-choose-an-erp-for-service-companies-key-factors-and-features/";s:11:"urlToAuthor";s:11:"/user/1148/";s:15:"POST_PROPERTIES";a:2:{s:4:"SHOW";s:1:"Y";s:4:"DATA";a:1:{s:16:"UF_BLOG_POST_DOC";a:22:{s:2:"ID";s:2:"96";s:9:"ENTITY_ID";s:9:"BLOG_POST";s:10:"FIELD_NAME";s:16:"UF_BLOG_POST_DOC";s:12:"USER_TYPE_ID";s:4:"file";s:6:"XML_ID";s:16:"UF_BLOG_POST_DOC";s:4:"SORT";s:3:"100";s:8:"MULTIPLE";s:1:"Y";s:9:"MANDATORY";s:1:"N";s:11:"SHOW_FILTER";s:1:"N";s:12:"SHOW_IN_LIST";s:1:"N";s:12:"EDIT_IN_LIST";s:1:"Y";s:13:"IS_SEARCHABLE";s:1:"Y";s:8:"SETTINGS";a:7:{s:4:"SIZE";i:20;s:10:"LIST_WIDTH";i:0;s:11:"LIST_HEIGHT";i:0;s:13:"MAX_SHOW_SIZE";i:0;s:16:"MAX_ALLOWED_SIZE";i:0;s:10:"EXTENSIONS";a:0:{}s:12:"TARGET_BLANK";s:1:"Y";}s:15:"EDIT_FORM_LABEL";s:16:"UF_BLOG_POST_DOC";s:17:"LIST